                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Hay</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Conger</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1904-03-12">
                            <hi rend="italic">March 12, 1904</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>(Mr. Hay instructs Mr. Conger to express to the minister for foreign affairs the
                    earnest hope of the United States Government that China will maintain strict
                    neutrality and that it will exercise proper care so that no provocation of any
                    sort be given to either of the belligerents.)</p>
            </div>
        </body>
